4. 问题: 近30天日均营业收入最高的前5个服务区是哪些？
   原始错误: 字段 b.service_area_id 不存在
LINE 1: ...ss_business_day_data b JOIN bss_service_area s ON b.service_...
                                                             ^
HINT:  也许您想要引用列"s.service_area_no"。
   修复后SQL:
   SELECT s.service_area_name AS 服务区名称, AVG(b.pay_sum) AS 日均营业收入 FROM bss_business_day_data b JOIN bss_service_area s ON b.service_no = s.service_area_no WHERE b.oper_date >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '30 days' GROUP BY s.service_area_name ORDER BY 日均营业收入 DESC LIMIT 5;
----------------------------------------

5. 问题: 餐饮类档口中，平均订单金额超过200元的有哪些？
   原始错误: 字段 b.branch_id 不存在
LINE 1: ...ROM bss_business_day_data b JOIN bss_branch br ON b.branch_i...
                                                             ^
HINT:  也许您想要引用列"b.branch_no"。
   修复后SQL:
   SELECT br.branch_name AS 档口名称, AVG(b.pay_sum / NULLIF(b.order_sum, 0)) AS 平均订单金额 FROM bss_business_day_data b JOIN bss_branch br ON b.branch_no = br.branch_no WHERE br.classify = '餐饮' AND b.order_sum > 0 GROUP BY br.branch_name HAVING AVG(b.pay_sum / NULLIF(b.order_sum, 0)) > 200 ORDER BY 平均订单金额 DESC;
----------------------------------------

